<td>Option</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>enter</code></td>
<td>Enter</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>back</code></td>
<td>Back</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>up</code></td>
<td>Swipe Up</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>down</code></td>
<td>Swipe Down</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>left</code></td>
<td>Swipe Left</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>right</code></td>
<td>Swipe Right</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
<h3>Cover Art Issues</h3>
<p>If you are running a game/title on your PS4 that does not display a cover or displays the incorrect cover, post an issue <a href="https://github.com/ktnrg45/pyps4-2ndscreen/issues">here</a>.</p>
<p>Be sure to include the following information:</p>
<ul>
<li>Your Country</li>
</ul>
<p>As well as the exact values for the following attributes found in the state of your PS4 entity.</p>
<ul>
<li>media_title</li>
<li>media_content_id</li>
</ul>
